ffmpeg -framerate 0.2 -start_number X -i image%02d.png -c:v libx264 -vf "scale=trunc(iw/2)*2:trunc(ih/2)*2" -pix_fmt yuv420p output.mp4
                  ^fps                   ^titles are imageXX.png        ^ensure's proper scaling

https://ffmpeg.org
https://trac.ffmpeg.org/wiki/Create%20a%20video%20slideshow%20from%20images
